kely crossings of nationalist and internationalist ideologies during the interwar period.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 0aMusicxPerformancexHistoryy20th century. 0aMusicxSocial aspects. 0aSingingzEnglandzLondonxHistoryy20th century. 0aSingingzNew York (State)zNew YorkxHistoryy20th century. 0aSongs, GermanxSocial aspects. 0aWorld War, 1914-1918xInfluence. 4ainterwar. 4alieder. 4aperformance. 4apolitics. 4ataste. 4atechnology. 4atransatlantic. 7aMUSIC / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press eBook Package 2016-2018z978311063537940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226563602423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226563602.jpg  a978-3-11-063537-9  University of Chicago Press eBook Package 2016-2018c2016d2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles